      "q": "Vantage Apparel is choosing how many temporary workers to schedule. Worker 1: MC $1,225, MR $1,770 Worker 2: MC $1,160, MR $1,420 Worker 3: MC $1,075, MR $1,050 Worker 4: MC $990, MR $545 Worker 5: MC $905, MR $320 Using marginal analysis, how many workers should be scheduled?",
